phrases: You have got some nerve, calling for our help.
Thanks to you, Ange escaped, and we lost the Villkiss.
You, the Knight of the Villkiss!
Without the Villkiss, we cannot defeat Embryo.
Your father was the one who taught us that.
You let it all go to waste.
Quite the dutiful son, are not you?
We ought to go help Ange.
When we can barely escape ourselves?
Besides, it is no use helping her.
She will not take my orders anymore.
I will inform you of our plans after we resupply.
Let Ange into the Diamond Rose Knighthood?
She is needed in order to change the world.
Ange will not listen to you, Embryo-sama.
I just need her to use, like a tool.
You are the one that is most important to me.
You will get in trouble if you do not obey your master.
Then refuse, no matter what he says.
I would never join your Daikon Radish Knighthood, anyway.
It is the Diamond Rose Knighthood.
Is that what you wanted to hear?
The tea Momoka prepares for me is hundreds of times better.
You did not call me to brag about your stupid tea, did you?
I will get straight to the point.
I would like to take you as my wife.
You are stronger, more intelligent and more beautiful than anyone I have ever met.
You are the goddess of the new world.
You are perfectly suited to be my wife.
So naturally, I want to grant my wife's wishes.
The people of the old world were barbaric and warlike.
In order to save the species, I had to recreate humanity.
I made an intelligent humanity, connected through advanced information technology.
I made a world of abundance, filled with light.
They became used to being given things,
and they stopped thinking for themselves.
They will hate and slaughter upon command.
You have seen their true, rotten nature.
Humanity has not changed at all.
They are fundamentally evil and foolish.
I am certain that a humanity that we created would be upright and good.
It is the laws that govern the universe, fashioned into a melody.
By amplifying this melody through the Ragna-mail and using Aura's energy,
we can merge the two worlds...
What you saw on the DRAGON world was merely a test of the process.
That will stop your weird magic tricks, right?
I would rather die than become your wife...
So you are the one to die!
But that is what makes you worthy of being my wife.
It seems even you cannot handle pain multiplied fifty times.
I turned all of her pain into pleasure.
Ange, it is easy for me to manipulate you.
If you do not want to suffer anymore, you will accept my proposal.
Bring her back to normal, please.
I am not in the mood.
If the commander is not going to, I will.
I made a promise with her.
That we will destroy this world together.
You love Ange, do not you?
We have known each other for a long time.
I am the same, too, after all.
I cannot seem to handle being without Chris.
I always felt like I had to protect her.
But she is so strong without me...
But I am still a total loser.
I was the one who needed Chris.
Let us go get them back.
Want me to get you out?
But in exchange, there is something I want you to help me with.
You have not done it with Ange yet, have you?
If it all works out, I will let you do me.
My first time will be with Ange I mean, no!
I mean, well, I am not indulging in sexy times until we are done fighting.
Like, as a knight, I want to avoid anything amorous.
I heard you had your face in Ange's crotch all the time.
I was not being a pervert!
So you are just a loser.
I want to go help Ange.
Something is wrong with our commander.
We cannot get out of the residential block.
Are you going to Embryo-sama's place or something?
You were talking in your sleep.
I will not let you go!
You have such a defiant attitude for a slave.
Think about what you have done!
I have not forgotten what you did with Julio-sama to hurt Angelise-sama.
You must not die until you do.
Underground the west wing of the royal palace,
He manipulated my mind and took everything from me.
My pride, my duty, my chastity...
the duty of freeing the Norma,
All of it was replaced by his love, by my dependence upon him,
and by the pleasures he gave me.
Why did not you tell us?
How was I supposed to explain?
That I went to kill Embryo,
but instead he took my body and mind?
That Libertus failed, that my friends died...
They all died trying to help a filthy woman like me.
There is only one thing I can do to grieve.
I am sure he is obsessed with his new toy about now.
This is our only chance to kill him.
That is why you tried to go alone.
I came along because it was you.
I followed you because you were my friend.
And I was just being used the whole time.
Now that we know what happened, we cannot let you continue being in charge.
You will not make my mistakes.
It is quite enjoyable to see beauty oppressed, suffering, and in despair.
This is what happens when you defy Embryo-sama.
You are the idiot who fell for that slimeball.
Embryo-sama is all I have left.
But that is not true of you.
You have the Villkiss, your friends, and your own place to be.
You are strong enough without having to transform.
Do not take anything else from me.
If you keep resisting, he will end up destroying your mind.
It is not like I am trying to help you or anything.
I just do not like seeing you be so pathetic.
Sing, sing, the two wishes are now,
Strongly, strongly shining in heavenly gold.
You will be less trouble if I make a daring escape.
I do not need your sympathy, you macho gorilla.
Guard the Dawn Tower until the mission is complete.
I suppose I will have to handle it.
You are not getting away, Ange.
I am here to repay you, Ange.
I am going to be so unlucky next week!
Next week, could we end up...
I thought this might be a death flag...
They will not kill us off!
